Description:
  Listopia generator will copy files for listopia tree in your web project

This text:
  bundle exec rails g listopia --help

Generators:
  bundle exec rails g listopia install

  This will create:
   config/initializers/listopia.rb
   app/controllers/lists_controller.rb
   app/controllers/list_items_controller.rb
	 app/models/list.rb
	 app/models/list_item.rb	

  bundle exec rails g listopia controllers

  This will create:
    app/controllers/lists_controller.rb
    app/controllers/list_items_controller.rb

  bundle exec rails g listopia models

  This will create:
		app/models/list.rb
		app/models/list_item.rb	


View Generators:
  bundle exec rails g listopia:views assets
  bundle exec rails g listopia:views helper
  bundle exec rails g listopia:views views

Migrations:
  bundle exec rake listopia_engine:install:migrations